\id 2CO - Sembeleke Samberigi PNG 2 CORINTH 01 22/3/91 Macnaughtan 
\h 2 KOTINDI 
\toc1 Polomaęž‰ Kotindi Siosi paęž‰taęž‰ yaapo peao tapaeyeke wapee 
\toc2 2 Kotindi 
\toc3 2 Kotindi 
\mt1 Polomaęž‰ Kotindi Siosi paęž‰taęž‰ yaapo peao tapaeyeke wapee  
\c 1  
\p
\v 1 Kodaęž‰naęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ Yesu Ketisonaęž‰ aposolo hali hano laęž‰laęž‰ hali IĚ± Polomaęž‰ make nikaęž‰ kame Timodimaęž‰ make tapaasopaęž‰ wape doe. Mo Kotindi da paęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ siosi paęž‰taęž‰ make mo Akaya kenke paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ alopaęž‰me.  
\v 2 Nikaęž‰ Apaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ make Tekehali Yesu Ketisomaęž‰ make iki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homa tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰eki make puki lopaniaasaęž‰eki make kinaęž‰e.   
\s1 Polomaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ keiyae leekeeki  
\p
\v 3 Niki paeyaomaęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰ nikaęž‰ Tekehali Yesu Ketisonaęž‰ Apaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ keiyae lomanaęž‰e. Ipikitaęž‰ pa hameke aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ Apaęž‰ hataęž‰ mo tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ ipu halaęž‰me.  
\v 4 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ nikaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰manu minolomaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ tambaęž‰ mu halaęž‰me. Pa ekipeke ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ niki tambaęž‰ miaęž‰eki mumaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ mo mandane kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰hali tambaęž‰ miomono paęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 5 Nikitaęž‰ mo hande Ketisonaęž‰ tandamanu putu polomaęž‰ tupaęž‰ kone Ketiso paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ aneke tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰eki putu polomaęž‰me.  
\v 6 Tanda nomaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ kototaęž‰ ikaęž‰ tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰eki make paęž‰taęž‰laęž‰laęž‰eki make minolomaęž‰me. Nikitaęž‰ tambaęž‰ miaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ iki make tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰me. Do hau manumaęž‰taęž‰ mo nikanaęž‰maęž‰ minolomaęž‰ homeke haupiki tandamanu ikanaęž‰maęž‰ make minelemeeki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ mo homu pea hataęž‰ kimaęž‰ na homaęž‰laęž‰eki anekemaęž‰ daenaęž‰ lelimikie.  
\v 7 Koto ekinaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ nikaęž‰ hone ti laalomaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ hone yaapo yaapo na ulumaęž‰me. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ nikaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰manu telipa mineleme ekinaęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ make nikaęž‰ tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰eki minolomaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ putupa minelememe laa hone witolomaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 8 Kame tonuo nikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo hande Eisia kenke paęž‰taęž‰ mumaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰manu iki paęž‰taęž‰ pa hone u tiaaluekemaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰me. Mo niki manda wiaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ manutaęž‰ tieke hombeleke make kaęž‰ndaęž‰ tieke piaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ nikitaęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ hanaĚ±laĚ±ęž‰ na piaęž‰me hone umaęž‰me.  
\v 9 Niki paęž‰taęž‰ homenaęž‰e alaęž‰ pitaęž‰ ambaęž‰ laęž‰ wiki nono piaęž‰me. Pate doeki piaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ nikaęž‰ homeke na ti lake pa mo homaęž‰laęž‰eki mea tiao halaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ homeke hone tulaamono piaęž‰me.  
\v 10 Dupiki otaęž‰ hoke paalaęž‰piki homaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu paęž‰taęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ niki tambaęž‰ miaęž‰ ekinaęž‰taęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ niki paa tambaęž‰ milieke laa nikaęž‰ honetaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ tulaalomaęž‰me.  
\v 11 Kutupa make niki tambaęž‰ minolo yeni peaasome ekimaęž‰taęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ niki pa tambaęž‰ minaęž‰ lelimikie. Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ nikinaęž‰ piteleme yeni paeyaotaęž‰ hombo pealieke. Kutupa Kodaęž‰maęž‰ niki epeaalieke. Koto ekinaęž‰ wopumaęž‰ nikinaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ keiyae lelimikie.   
\s1 Pulueke laa laęž‰ wieke ekitaęž‰ paa topo piekeeki  
\p
\v 12 Nikaęž‰ honemaęž‰ otaęž‰ hau pelememe laa peneme yaasekenaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolomaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ dupae. Nikaęž‰ pitolomaęž‰ hau paeyao paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ kitaęž‰laęž‰ yakopiki hau make tikitiki piki hau make pitolomaęž‰me. Dupiki hau manutaęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ hone u lenkenaęž‰ peaasaęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ na aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me. Pate mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homa tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ homeke pumaęž‰me Dupiki haumanu pumaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ pumaęž‰pate pa iki paęž‰taęž‰ homeke hone wopu witolo hataęž‰ pumaęž‰me.  
\v 13-14 Nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ yataęž‰polo hataęž‰ hone ulu pelemeeki homeke laa tapaasomaęž‰me. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ nikitaęž‰ hosiki siki hone ulumaęž‰pate yaka hone paęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ nikitaęž‰ hone wopu wilimikie. Pa ekipeke mo nikaęž‰ Tekehali Yesunaęž‰ Natenaęž‰taęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ ikinaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolo polomaęž‰ tupaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ make nikinaęž‰ homeke hau kone pilimikie.   
\p
\v 15 IĚ±taęž‰ doeki manunaęž‰ hone lenkipaęž‰ witolotaęž‰ iki yaapo peao epeaenaęž‰ honemaęž‰ iki handolo ipuluekemaęž‰ hone pambao uaęž‰me.  
\v 16 IĚ± mo Diudia nane puaęž‰peke ekinaęž‰ tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu maęž‰ndaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ yaka hone pambao witolotaęž‰ mo Maęž‰sedonia nane yopulu make pa laęž‰kaęž‰la ipulu make iki handaęž‰ tia ipulueke hone uaęž‰me.  
\v 17 Doeki hone pambao witolotaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ hone topo topo pu halo some hone wimipe. IĚ±maęž‰ yaka hone pambaasotaęž‰ mo kenke haunaęž‰ IĚ± IĚ± alo hataęž‰ aoma aoma make diaęž‰maęž‰ma diaęž‰maęž‰ma pitaęž‰ homeke dinaęž‰ lo halope.  
\v 18 Otaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi homeke lo halaęž‰ ekinaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ laęž‰ uaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ mo aowe make diaęž‰me pi yaapo na laęž‰ uaęž‰me.  
\v 19 Pa ekipeke mo Yesu Ketiso Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Eiyeke hande Sailasimaęž‰ make Timodimaęž‰ make IĚ±maęž‰ make iki paęž‰taęž‰ hande walomaęž‰ hali ipikitaęž‰ aowe make diaęž‰me hali diaęž‰me. Otaęž‰ diaęž‰yaęž‰laęž‰pate ipikitaęž‰ otaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Aowe homekee.  
\v 20 Pa ekipeke Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi laęž‰ ulaęž‰ ekimanu paeyaotaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ Aowe laęž‰laęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ biki tieke winaęž‰ loluekemaęž‰taęž‰ nikaęž‰ Kutu pinaęž‰e. Keiyae pitaęž‰ Yesu Ketiso paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ alomaęž‰me.  
\v 21 Kodaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ homeke niki iki ameĚ±leĚ± Ketiso paęž‰taęž‰ tunaalomaęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ nikaęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ wia halomaęž‰me laa hone lenkipa wiomono alaęž‰me.  
\v 22 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ kone niki maĚ±leke lilaęž‰me. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ombu nikitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ ekie laataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ tombo niki paęž‰taęž‰ ulaęž‰me. Kodaęž‰maęž‰ mo niki paęž‰taęž‰ kaęž‰laęž‰ Holi Sipitiditaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wetepenaęž‰ kulu paęž‰laęž‰ ale paeyaonaęž‰ titinaęž‰ tombo kaęž‰laęž‰mee.   
\p
\v 23 Kodaęž‰taęž‰ yaka wekitisi hali lonoe. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ yaka honetaęž‰ hone ulaęž‰me. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ iki kaęž‰ndaęž‰ kiaęž‰peke yeketaęž‰ Kotindi nane pao na poaęž‰me.  
\v 24 Nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone tulaalemeeki manutaęž‰ dupi dupi alo diaęž‰me. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ hone tulaaseme ekitaęž‰ ambaęž‰ koto honkopu hao wia haleme handaęž‰e. Koto ekinaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ iki taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homelemeeki mea aęž‰paaluekemaęž‰ iki ameĚ±leĚ± apaęž‰tao e pokolomaęž‰me.   
\c 2  
\p
\v 1 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ yaka hone witolotaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ homaapaęž‰naęž‰ pao na ipulueke hone uaęž‰me.  
\v 2 Pa ekipeke IĚ±maęž‰ ikaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ homaęž‰ tiawaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ yolutaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ IĚ± taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰ tiaalo piaęž‰pe. Otaęž‰ mo hande ikaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ homawaęž‰ tapake homeke yolo piaęž‰me.  
\v 3 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ koto tameiyaęž‰ tapaowaęž‰me. Pa ekipeke IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰pa yaka taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰ tiaapeke yaęž‰laęž‰ tapakemaęž‰ kone IĚ± puki kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homo tiaaseme laa laapaęž‰naęž‰ alo puaęž‰me. IĚ±maęž‰ hone witolotaęž‰ IĚ± taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolo dinaęž‰taęž‰ iki paeyao make taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homelememe.  
\v 4 Iki paęž‰taęž‰ tameiyaęž‰ tapaowaęž‰taęž‰ yaka puki kaęž‰ndaęž‰ tieke pitolo hataęž‰ tanda tieke piaęž‰me. Kutupa eĚ± wopu loaęž‰me. Mo tameiyaęž‰ tapaowaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ teketaęž‰ ikaęž‰ puki kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homaaluekemaęž‰ na puaęž‰pate ikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homoloeki hone uemenaęž‰yeke puaęž‰me.   
\s1 Hoke hau paęž‰laęž‰ halinaęž‰ hoke hau paeyaasaęž‰eki  
\p
\v 5 Maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ puki kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰ tiaeyaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ na piaęž‰pate iki paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ putupa kiaęž‰me alome. Koto kaęž‰ndaęž‰ putupa kiaęž‰me pi alo ekitaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ mo some lombei piki tupaęž‰ hando lapeke yeke alome.  
\v 6 Iki wopumaęž‰ hande some dupiki tupaęž‰ panisi peaeme ekitaęž‰ anaęž‰e.  
\v 7 Ametaęž‰ epeke ekitaęž‰ mo somemaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ Ketiso minaęž‰paęž‰laapaęž‰naęž‰ iki paeyaomaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hoke hau pa paeyao epeke hau pinaęž‰ sutiaapaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 8 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homelemeeki otaęž‰ peneme yaapaęž‰peke laa honke alome.  
\v 9 IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ koto tameiyaęž‰ tapaowaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ mo hande la handaęž‰laęž‰eki kuaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ekipa bepolaalimipe la handuluekemaęž‰ puaęž‰me. Kutupa ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ hoto paeyao yaka alo ekimanu koto kone opua pilimio la handuluekemaęž‰ puaęž‰me.  
\v 10 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ hali maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰eki pa paeyawaemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ make pa paeyawalueke. Maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ pa paeyaapeke ekitaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ pa paeyaapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me hone uaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ iki hoeyaapaęž‰naęž‰yeke IĚ±maęž‰ Ketisonaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ hataęž‰ pu halome.  
\v 11 Kutu pu halo ekinaęž‰ teketaęž‰ mo Sadanimaęž‰ niki bepolaamaęž‰naęž‰ loaęž‰me. Pa ekipeke nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hoke hone pambao ulaęž‰eki manutaęž‰ ambaęž‰ hone ulumaęž‰me.   
\s1 Polomaęž‰ Dotoaęž‰si da paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ hone kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homeekeeki  
\p
\v 12 IĚ± mo Dotoaęž‰si da paęž‰taęž‰ Ketisonaęž‰ Pi Seliapo waluekemaęž‰ opolo puaataęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰ pokolo puaęž‰ etaęž‰ mo Tekehalimaęž‰ ambaęž‰ potaęž‰ wiayekeeki handaęž‰ uaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 13  Pate IĚ±taęž‰ pomo tieke piaęž‰me. Pa ekipeke nikaęž‰ kame Taitasitaęž‰ na handaęž‰ u hao loaęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ Aęž‰taloe laa mo Maęž‰sedonia nane poaęž‰me.   
\s1 Ketiso paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ bepolaapaęž‰pekeeki  
\p
\v 14 Kutu puaęž‰pate Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ keiyae lomanaęž‰e. Pa ekipeke Ketiso paęž‰taęž‰ apaęž‰tao halomaęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ nikitaęž‰ Ketisonaęž‰ bepolaalaęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ dipula wandaęž‰hali leke samaęž‰ titinaęž‰ hatuku pu halaęž‰me. Mo Ketiso hone witaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ e pokolo hataęž‰ mo hande totopopiki ale putu paęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ kenke honiki paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ putu paęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 15 Nikitaęž‰ mo hande Ketisomaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰laęž‰ totopopiki alemaęž‰ handolomaęž‰me. Koto aletaęž‰ mo daęž‰taasaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali make alu paęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰hali ankaęž‰lopunaęž‰ putupu halaęž‰ alemaęž‰ handolomaęž‰me.  
\v 16 Mo alu paęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰hali lu homaasaęž‰ tandepeke punkupiki alemaęž‰ handaęž‰laęž‰me. Pate mo detenaęž‰yeke paęž‰taęž‰laęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali daęž‰taapeke yaęž‰laęž‰ totopopiki ale ipulaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ handaęž‰laęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ dupiki kaęž‰ndaęž‰piki e pokaaluekemaęž‰taęž‰ epitaęž‰ anaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰pe.  
\v 17 Nikitaęž‰ mo hande mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pitaęž‰ mo bisinisi peaęž‰peke alesiki leke pu haleme tupaęž‰ na pu halomaęž‰pate Kodaęž‰maęž‰ niki tapaalaęž‰ ekinaęž‰taęž‰ nikitaęž‰ Ketisonaęž‰ e pokaasaęž‰ haliweki hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ tikitiki yao poko halomaęž‰me.   
\c 3  
\s1 Panake pinaęž‰ e pokaęž‰laęž‰ haliweki  
\p
\v 1 Do alo ekitaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ nikaęž‰ kone biki pa minaęž‰liake nono paęž‰laęž‰pe. O mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ piteleme tupaęž‰ mo biki epeaasaęž‰ tameiyaęž‰manu iki paęž‰taęž‰ kiomonope o iki paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ miomonope.  
\v 2 Diaęž‰me iki kone nikaęž‰ wape pea ulaęž‰ tameiyaęž‰e. Paeyaomaęž‰ yataęž‰pa hone winaęž‰yeke ikitaęž‰ nikaęž‰ pukinaęž‰ wape pea ulaęž‰me.  
\v 3 Ketiso ipikaęž‰ kone do tameiyaęž‰ lao niki paęž‰taęž‰ tapaalaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ penemenaęž‰ ulaęž‰me. Do tameiyaęž‰taęž‰ halinaęž‰ kikimaęž‰ na laalaęž‰pate mo deto halaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Sipitidimaęž‰ laalaęž‰me. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo toopi sasakenaęž‰ na laalaęž‰pate wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ puki manunaęž‰ laalaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 4 Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ doeki alome ekitaęž‰ Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ ambaęž‰ hone baalomaęž‰me.  
\v 5 Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ anaęž‰naęž‰ kone do etaęž‰ pokaalumeke pi lapeketaęž‰ otaęž‰ waleke maęž‰ndaęž‰ na ulaęž‰me. Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ peaęž‰peke honkoputaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ ipulaęž‰me.  
\v 6 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ do panake laęž‰ ulaęž‰ pi paęž‰taęž‰ e pokomono niki wele peaasaęž‰me. Do panake laęž‰ ulaęž‰ pitaęž‰ mo wape pea ulaęž‰ Lo Pi diaęž‰yaęž‰laęž‰pate pa mo Sipitidimaęž‰ peaasaęž‰ekie. Mo wape pea ulaęž‰ Lo pimaęž‰taęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki mea ipulaęž‰pate pa mo Sipitidimaęž‰taęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰eki kitaęž‰laęž‰me.   
\p
\v 7 Mo Mosesinaęž‰ Lo Pitaęž‰ toopi sasakenaęž‰ wape pea lao haleaęž‰ dinaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± opolo epeekeme. Kutupa koto Mosesinaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ piaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ±taęž‰ paa alu putia peaęž‰pate kone honkopu wopu piaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ mo Isulai wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ ipiki na handaake wimikime. Mo homaęž‰laęž‰eki mea ipulaęž‰ Lo Pitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ e pokaęž‰laęž‰ dinaęž‰ dupiki paĚ±aĚ± paęž‰laęž‰eki mea aęž‰paęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me hone umaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰  
\v 8 kotaęž‰ mo Sipitidinaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰ haumanu paęž‰taęž‰ ipulaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ±taęž‰ ekipiki paĚ±aĚ± tieke paęž‰laęž‰pe hone umanaęž‰e.  
\v 9 Mo hoke yenki mea ipulaęž‰ Lo Pinaęž‰ hautaęž‰ otaęž‰ yole piaęž‰pate pa mo daęž‰taapeke paęž‰taęž‰laęž‰laęž‰eki mea aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ lombei pikieki yole paęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 10 Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ dupa lapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me. Ame do otaęž‰ lombei piki paĚ±aĚ± wopu paęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ mo ambaęž‰ hande paĚ±aĚ± wopu pieke ekitaęž‰ alu paęž‰laęž‰me lapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 11 Kutupa mo ambaęž‰ hande nate leke hosiki hokulunaęž‰ pa wieke ekinaęž‰taęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± piekeme lomaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo ame do honiki na wiki otaęž‰ hao halaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ±taęž‰ otaęž‰ lombei peaake paĚ±aĚ± paęž‰laęž‰me laa hone umanaęž‰e.   
\p
\v 12 Nikitaęž‰ do hone tulao handeteke halomaęž‰eki wia halomaęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ nikitaęž‰ honkopu wopu halomaęž‰me.  
\v 13 Nikitaęž‰ mo hande Mosesi tupaęž‰ diaęž‰me. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo Isulai wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± tieke piaęž‰eki alu paeyaęž‰eki handaamaęž‰naęž‰ yeke ipikaęž‰ leke popeleketaęž‰ dau sinkipiki maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ aęž‰mbeeke tupaęž‰ diaęž‰me.  
\v 14 Ikaęž‰ hone manutaęž‰ otaęž‰ aęž‰mbao pambeekeme. Kutupa aęž‰pa otaęž‰ ame do natenaęž‰ make mo hande ambaęž‰ Lo pi lao wieke bukamanu yataęž‰pelemeketaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone manutaęž‰ mo hande dau sinkipiki maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ aęž‰mbaalaęž‰me. Maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ Ketiso paęž‰taęž‰ tunaeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ homeketaęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo leke popeleke aęž‰mbaalaęž‰ dau sinkipiki maęž‰ndaęž‰ mea baapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 15 Otaęž‰ ame do make mo Mosesinaęž‰ Lo Pi yataęž‰pelemeketaęž‰ mo dau sinkipikimaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone manutaęž‰ paa aęž‰mbao halaęž‰me.  
\v 16 Pate anaęž‰naęž‰ mea baapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me. Pa ekipeke mo Baibolomaęž‰ Mosesi hotiolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ipikaęž‰ leke popeleke aęž‰mbaalaęž‰ dau sinkipiki mea bake hautaęž‰ ipiki Tekehali paęž‰taęž‰ laęž‰kaęž‰la peaęž‰ dinaęž‰ piaęž‰me laęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ loaęž‰me.  
\v 17 Koto Tekehali paęž‰taęž‰e laęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ mo Sipitidi paęž‰taęž‰ konee laęž‰laęž‰me. Kutupa mo Tekehalinaęž‰ Sipitidi halaęž‰ ale paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ kaęž‰laęž‰paęž‰ tapaasaęž‰ hau ulaęž‰me.  
\v 18 Kotaęž‰ niki paeyaotaęž‰ mo Tekehalinaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ±taęž‰ na aęž‰mbake nikaęž‰ leke popelekemaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ±naęž‰ suĚ±aĚ± suĚ±aĚ± walomaęž‰me. Kutupa koto homeke paĚ±aĚ±maęž‰ kone Tekehali hande Sipitidi paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ ipulaęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ nikitaęž‰ mo hoto paeyao pa daeyaęž‰tiki pu halaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± tieke paęž‰taęž‰ ipikimaęž‰ handomono topo peao halaęž‰me.   
\c 4  
\s1 Kanake paęž‰taęž‰ ti teke pambo ulaęž‰eki  
\p
\v 1 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homa tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰ hali hataęž‰ niki do e pokomono kaęž‰laęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ do e paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰manu ipulaęž‰pate niki ki hone na ulumaęž‰me.  
\v 2 Nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo aęž‰mbaasaęž‰ haumanu make yaalaęž‰piki haumanu make hoe nane winaęž‰ lolomaęž‰me. Nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ makeaasaęž‰ haumanu na pu halomaęž‰me. Kutupa Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi walolo hataęž‰taęž‰ ataęž‰kaęž‰ peake tupaęž‰ na walo halomaęž‰me. Nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ hataęž‰ mo otaęž‰ pitaęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ opitolo hataęž‰taęž‰ epeke tupaęž‰ walelememe alo haenaęž‰ peneme yao walo halomaęž‰me.  
\v 3 Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ peneme yao walolomaęž‰ Pi Seliapotaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰mbao wiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo alupaęž‰laęž‰ potaęž‰naęž‰ polo peleme wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ homeke aęž‰mbao ulaęž‰me.  
\v 4 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ hone na tulaasememe. Pa ekipeke do kenkenaęž‰ hoke kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone manutaęž‰ timbaęž‰ laęž‰ pambaenaęž‰ halaęž‰me. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo ikinaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± peaapeke paĚ±aĚ±taęž‰ handaamaęž‰naęž‰ yeke saęž‰saęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰me. Mo Ketiso otaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ handeke halinaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ±naęž‰ mo Pi Seliapo paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ ipulaęž‰eki handaamaęž‰naęž‰ yeke pitaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 5 Nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ nikinaęž‰ na walolomaęž‰pate pa Yesu Ketisotaęž‰ Tekehalie laa nikitaęž‰ walolomaęž‰me. Kutupa Yesunaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pa hameke e pokaasomaęž‰ haliwekie laa walolomaęž‰me.  
\v 6 Mo ambaęž‰ hande Kodaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo timbaęž‰ laęž‰ pambaęž‰laęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ mo paĚ±aĚ± paęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± pinaęž‰e leeke homeke Kodaęž‰maęž‰ kone mo paĚ±aĚ±taęž‰ nikaęž‰ pukinaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± peayaęž‰me. Kotaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ±taęž‰ Ketisonaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ hone wiomonoyeke paĚ±aĚ± peaalaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 7 Koto paęž‰laęž‰pate kone do hande otaęž‰ epeke ti teke witaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ pa nikitaęž‰ mo hande pa baasaęž‰ kanake paęž‰taęž‰ kone pamba ulaęž‰me. Kutu pieke haunaęž‰ teketaęž‰ mo honkopu tieketaęž‰ nikaęž‰eki diaęž‰yaęž‰laęž‰pate Kodaęž‰naęž‰ ekie laa waluekemaęž‰ piaęž‰me.  
\v 8 Nikitaęž‰ hoto maęž‰ndaęž‰ ninaęž‰taęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homo halomaęž‰pate otaęž‰ lu tumbaaso diaęž‰me. Hoto maęž‰ndaęž‰ ninaęž‰taęž‰ hone eleke eleke u halomaęž‰pate nikaęž‰ hone pua dokaęž‰tiki yaalaęž‰ dinaęž‰taęž‰ pa pinaęž‰e hone na u halomaęž‰me.  
\v 9 Aęž‰ndaęž‰ tunkuliki hali wopu halemepate nikitaęž‰ yankeke ameĚ±leĚ± ombu halomaęž‰me. Kutupa nate maęž‰ndaęž‰ ninaęž‰taęž‰ oni kenkenaęž‰ lu lopao halemepate nikitaęž‰ otaęž‰ na hoyo halomaęž‰me.  
\v 10 Hoto paeyaotaęž‰ nikaęž‰ kenke lokenaęž‰taęž‰ mo Yesunaęž‰ homeekeeki meatia pomu halomaęž‰me. Pa ekipeke nikaęž‰ loke paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ ipiki daęž‰ta halaęž‰eki handenaęž‰yeke loaęž‰me.  
\v 11 Yesunaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ nikaęž‰ hatia pulumaęž‰ ale paęž‰taęž‰ manutaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki teke paęž‰taęž‰ hao halomaęž‰me. Pa ekipeke ipikaęž‰ deto halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ nikaęž‰ do kenke loke paęž‰taęž‰ handenaęž‰yeke pitolomaęž‰me.  
\v 12 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ e pokaęž‰laęž‰pate pa daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ e pokaęž‰laęž‰me.   
\p
\v 13 Mo Baibolomaęž‰ alotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ pi loaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ teketaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ hone tulaowaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ puaęž‰me laęž‰laęž‰me. Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ make homeke hone tulaasaęž‰ haumaęž‰ dupa alomaęž‰me. Mo lomaęž‰eki manunaęž‰ teketaęž‰ nikaęž‰ hone tulaomaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ pumaęž‰me.  
\v 14 Mo hande Tekehali Yesu mea daęž‰taeyaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ niki make Yesu taapu mea daęž‰taalieke hone ulumaęž‰me. Kutupa iki ameĚ±leĚ± mandakenaęž‰ ipiki halaęž‰ alenaęž‰ hatuku pelieke.  
\v 15 Doeki paeyaotaęž‰ ikaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ peaasaęž‰me. Kutupa Kodaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homa tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ pulu hataęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ make Kodaęž‰ pataęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± wopu minaęž‰ keiyae alaęž‰ yenimanu hakaęž‰taęž‰pao pu halimikie.   
\s1 Hone tulaasaęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰eki  
\p
\v 16 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰manu epenaęž‰ kone ki hone na ulumaęž‰me. Nikaęž‰ manda loketaęž‰ koke yomo yomo pitaęž‰laęž‰pate nikaęž‰ temokotaęž‰ hoto paeyao wamo peaęž‰tiki pu halaęž‰me.  
\v 17 Kutupa do hosiki pa taęž‰kaęž‰li minolomaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ manumaęž‰taęž‰ koto kaęž‰ndaęž‰ otaęž‰ lombeipiki pa u halopaęž‰laęž‰ seliapo piki paĚ±aĚ± mea ipilieke.  
\v 18 Nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ nikaęž‰ leke wia halomaęž‰eki manutaęž‰ mo lekemaęž‰ handaęž‰peke ale manunaęž‰ diaęž‰yaęž‰laęž‰pate pa mo lekemaęž‰ na handaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰ ale manunaęž‰ pu halomaęž‰me. Mo lekemaęž‰ handaęž‰peke ale manutaęž‰ nate leke hosiki sikinaęž‰ ulu paęž‰laęž‰pate pa mo lekemaęž‰ na handaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰ ale manutaęž‰ hoto paeyao otaęž‰ pa u halieke.   
\c 5  
\p
\v 1 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ dupa hone ulumaęž‰me. Do nikaęž‰ halomaęž‰ palai dataęž‰ nikaęž‰ kenke loke yalo hataęž‰ leisiyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ niki hao hapeke da oli hepeni wialieke. Mo dataęž‰ otaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ kone aęž‰eyaataęž‰ hoto paeyao pa hao halieke.  
\v 2 Kutupa ametaęž‰ nikaęž‰ we pambaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ oli hepeni nanemaęž‰ ipulaęž‰ dataęž‰ niki manda winaęž‰e laa hone wotu witolomaęž‰me.  
\v 3 Mo ekimaęž‰ dau leke yamomaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ nikitaęž‰ loke diaęž‰yaęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰hali na halumeke.  
\v 4 Niki do kenkenaęž‰ palai da paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰taęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ wese lo halomaęž‰me. Do ekitaęž‰ mo nikaęž‰ kenke loke mea baaluekemaęž‰ diaęž‰yaęž‰laęž‰pate nikaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ mo hepeninaęž‰eki nikinaęž‰ pambaenaęž‰yeke lomaęž‰me. Pa ekipeke mo homo halaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ da pandaęž‰ meakaęž‰naęž‰ bepolalieke.  
\v 5 Dupiki topo pulu paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ niki tikitiki yaasaęž‰me. Kutupa ipikaęž‰ Sipitiditaęž‰ mo wetepenaęž‰ niki kulu paęž‰laęž‰ alenaęž‰ peneme yaasaęž‰ tombo ulaęž‰eki kaęž‰laęž‰me.   
\p
\v 6 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ nikitaęž‰ hoto paeyao hali au la hataęž‰ honkopu hao halomaęž‰me. Nikitaęž‰ do nikaęž‰ lokenaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ pa hataęž‰ kone mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ da papate halomaęž‰me laa hone ulumaęž‰me.  
\v 7 Pa ekipeke nikaęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ lekemaęž‰ handaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ diaęž‰yaęž‰laęž‰pate hone tulaasaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ homekee.  
\v 8 Nikitaęž‰ hali au la hataęž‰ honkopu hao halomaęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ nikaęž‰ honemaęž‰ do nikaęž‰ lokenaęž‰ dataęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰lao mo Tekehali ameĚ±leĚ± oli da pua hao hawee hone ulumaęž‰me.  
\v 9 Pate nikaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ hau paeyaonaęž‰ titinaęž‰ hau homeketaęž‰ dupae. Ame do halomaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ make oli polo polomaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ make mo Tekehali taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaapeke hau homeke puluekemaęž‰ taapo halomaęž‰me.  
\v 10 Pa ekipeke niki paeyaotaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ pi yokaalu pinaęž‰ Ketisonaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ pua hapeke yaęž‰lieke. Homeke homekemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ meaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ milieke. Ipikaęž‰ kenke lokemaęž‰ epekeeki o hokeeki paęž‰laęž‰eki paeyao sikinaęž‰ anaęž‰naęž‰ kone milieke.   
\s1 Ketiso paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ yankeke hasaęž‰eki  
\p
\v 11 Kodaęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ hone ulumaęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mandane wandaęž‰hali hone laęž‰kaęž‰laluekemaęž‰ taapo halomaęž‰me. Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ nikaęž‰ hau paeyaosiki hone wopu ulaęž‰eki yalo yaka honemaęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ make ikaęž‰ temokomaęž‰ IĚ± make hone witolo pelememe.  
\v 12 Nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ nikaęž‰ biki paa minaęž‰liamenaęž‰ loluekemaęž‰ na taapolomaęž‰pate pa ikanaęž‰maęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ nikinaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ epeke pimanu la haloemenaęž‰ yeke taapolomaęž‰me. Dupiki hautaęž‰ mo halinaęž‰ otaęž‰ hau minaęž‰paęž‰lao pa manda lokenaęž‰ epeke hau handolo biki minaęž‰liaasaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ anaęž‰naęž‰ hombo pealo peleme ekinaęž‰ loaęž‰me.  
\v 13 Nikitaęž‰ kea tikitiki pumaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰eki kone peaaso pitolomaęž‰me. Make nikaęž‰ honemaęž‰ kesemaęž‰ pumaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikaęž‰eki kone peaaso pitolomaęž‰me.  
\v 14 Ketisonaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ niki handeteke halaęž‰me. Pa ekipeke nikanaęž‰maęž‰ hone witolotaęž‰ hali homekemaęž‰taęž‰ paeyaonaęž‰ homaeyekeme. Koto haumaęž‰taęž‰ paeyaomaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki putu pelememe.  
\v 15 Ipikitaęž‰ paeyaonaęž‰ homeeke ekitaęž‰ pa mo daęž‰ta haleme wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone na halo pelemepate pa ikinaęž‰ mo homa paa tiao daęž‰taęž‰laęž‰ hali paęž‰taęž‰ haenaęž‰yeke paęž‰laęž‰me.   
\p
\v 16 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ ametaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ manda haunaęž‰ dupiki somee dupiki somee pi na alomaęž‰me. Kenke hali tupaęž‰ mo nate maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ Ketisotaęž‰ dupiki somee o mukutu piki somee lomaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ametaęž‰ kotoeki otaęž‰ pa na alomaęž‰me.  
\v 17 Maęž‰ndaęž‰ epitaęž‰ Ketiso paęž‰taęž‰ tunaeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ panake some halaęž‰me. Ambaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ pulu hataęž‰ panakeeki aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me.   
\p
\v 18 Doeki paeyaotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ pealaęž‰me. Kototaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ Ketiso paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ nikitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ tunkuliki wandaęž‰hali topo pea yankekemanu hamono laęž‰laęž‰me. Kutupa nikanaęž‰maęž‰ mandane wandaęž‰hali ipikaęž‰ yankeke au laamono koto e tieke kaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 19 Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ walolomaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyaotaęž‰ Ketiso paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ yankeke au laalaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ alomaęž‰me. Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ iki pi yokaalu puluekemaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hoke hau na yataęž‰peaęž‰me. Kutupa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali ipikaęž‰ yankekemanu au lao halaęž‰ pitaęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ la kiaęž‰me.  
\v 20 Koto ekinaęž‰ ametaęž‰ niki do Ketisonaęž‰ pi lawaaso handaęž‰e. Kodaęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ homu tolumaęž‰ wi laęž‰laęž‰eki kone peneme yaasaęž‰me. Nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ Ketisonaęž‰ pi laaso hataęž‰ wi alomaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ dupae. Kodaęž‰maęž‰ iki aęž‰ndaęž‰ tunkuliki wandaęž‰hali halemeeki topo peao ipikaęž‰ yankeke au laenaęž‰ lapee lo halomaęž‰me.  
\v 21 Ketiso paęž‰taęž‰ hoke hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ na wiaęž‰pate kone nikaęž‰ epeke hau peaaso hataęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ nikaęž‰ hoke hau putupaęž‰ minaęž‰ leekeme. Pa ekipeke nikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki ameĚ±leĚ± tunaasotaęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ tikitiki paęž‰laęž‰eki putu pomono yeke paęž‰laęž‰me.   
\c 6  
\p
\v 1 Koto ekinaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰ ameĚ±leĚ± e pokaasomaęž‰ tapake hataęž‰ iki Kodaęž‰naęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homa tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰eki meleme wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ do meleme hautaęž‰ na hoeyaapaęž‰peke laa honke alomaęž‰me.  
\v 2 Do Kodaęž‰maęž‰ alaęž‰eki opie.  
\q1 Mo iki paęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰eki walo puaęž‰ nate epeeketaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ iki opuaęž‰me.  
\q1 Mo iki petelolo puaęž‰ nate opolo epeeketaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ iki tambaęž‰ muaęž‰me laa laęž‰laęž‰me.  
\m Opie. Do nate leketaęž‰ otaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ anaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰eki mulu peleme nate lekee. Ame do natetaęž‰ iki petelo paęž‰laęž‰ natee.   
\p
\v 3 Nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ nikaęž‰ pokolomaęž‰ enaęž‰ ataęž‰kaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰eki maęž‰ndaęž‰ na handaęž‰ winaęž‰e hone ulumaęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mandane wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ potaęž‰naęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ haĚ±laĚ±ęž‰mbaęž‰ liaenaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ uluekemaęž‰ na taapo halomaęž‰me.  
\v 4 Kotoeki na pikitaęž‰ nikaęž‰ pitolomaęž‰ hau paeyao paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ nikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ e pokaasomaęž‰ haliwekie laa dupa peneme yao halomaęž‰me. Mo walolo hataęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu make tanda tieke paęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu make mamatalaęž‰ ekimanu paęž‰taęž‰ make ki hone na wiki homu pea yu wia hao halomaęž‰me.  
\v 5 Nikitaęž‰ yombua baeme ekimanu make dipula mea lopaeme ekimanu make nate maęž‰ndaęž‰ ninaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali wopumaęž‰ mineke pankolo hataęž‰ niki hopiliaaso hataęž‰ hoke tetopiki pimanu wopu lememe. Kutupa make hakaęž‰taęž‰pao e pokomaęž‰ ekimanu make u na polumaęž‰ ekimanu make ne na nomaęž‰eki make wopu puaęž‰me.  
\v 6 Kutupa nikaęž‰ tikitiki piki hau pumaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ make nikaęž‰ hone manumaęž‰ make nikaęž‰ homu pea yu wia haomaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ make homu pitolo puki halomaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ make paeyaomaęž‰taęž‰ nikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ e pokaasomaęž‰ haliwekie laa walomaęž‰me. Kototaęž‰ nikaęž‰ otaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homomaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ make Holi Sipitidimaęž‰ make  
\v 7 mo otaęž‰ pi walomaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ make Kodaęž‰naęž‰ honkopumaęž‰ make paeyaomaęž‰ pumaęž‰me. Nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ nikaęž‰ tikitiki piki hau pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ mo aęž‰ndaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰ kolepe aęž‰ndeli pitaęž‰ hankaęž‰ yaapomaęž‰ handaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 8 Nate maęž‰ndaęž‰ ninaęž‰taęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ yeiyaęž‰ laasaęž‰ hau pu haleme make yaalaęž‰ peaasaęž‰ hau make pu halememe. Kutupa make kitata pu haleme make nikaęž‰ biki mea minaęž‰liao halememe. Kutupa make nikitaęž‰ yayapiki pi lo haleme haliwekie lo halemepate nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi homeke lo halomaęž‰me.  
\v 9 Nikitaęž‰ hone na wiki nono pelemepate nikitaęž‰ paeyaomaęž‰ hone wilimime. Nikitaęž‰ homelememe lo halemepate pa halomaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone wilimime. Nikitaęž‰ panisi peao halemepate kone niki homomono na lilimime.  
\v 10 Nikitaęž‰ puki hoeyao halemepate hoto paeyao taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolomaęž‰me. Nikitaęž‰ nate hali hake nono polomaęž‰pate nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mandane wandaęž‰hali wopu hamoko haenaęž‰ alomaęž‰me. Nikitaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ na wia hake nono polomaęž‰pate nikitaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ paeyao anaęž‰naęž‰ kone wia halomaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 11 Kotindi haleme yankeke tonuo. Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ nikinaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ pa kaęž‰laęž‰paęž‰ tapao otaęž‰ la kumaęž‰me. Nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ nikaęž‰ puki manutaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ anekemaęž‰ ku halomaęž‰me.  
\v 12 Nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ niki pukimanu iki paęž‰taęž‰ na aęž‰mbo halomaęž‰pate kone pa ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ pukimanu niki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰mbo halememe.  
\v 13 Ametaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ ikitaęž‰ yaka wekiwandiki tupaęž‰ leke iki paęž‰taęž‰ pi alome. Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homolomaęž‰ tupaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ make ikaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homelemeeki niki paęž‰taęž‰ walaęž‰pee. Ikaęž‰ pukimanu anekemaęž‰ lombaęž‰paęž‰peke.   
\s1 Pi na miki tapakenaęž‰ haunaęž‰ kinki pitaęž‰laęž‰eki  
\p
\v 14 Mo hone na tulaleme wandaęž‰hali ameĚ±leĚ± apaęž‰tao e pokuluekemaęž‰ na taapaęž‰peke. Pa ekipeke iki otaęž‰ taęž‰maęž‰ni peaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me. Tikitiki hau pitaęž‰laęž‰eki pitaęž‰ ataęž‰kaęž‰ piki hau pitaęž‰laęž‰eki yaapotaęž‰ ekipa yankeke hapeke yaęž‰laęž‰pe. PaĚ±aĚ± paęž‰laęž‰eki pitaęž‰ timbaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰eki yaapotaęž‰ ekipa apaęž‰tao hapeke yaęž‰laęž‰pe.  
\v 15 Kutupa Ketiso pitaęž‰ Sadani yaapomaęž‰taęž‰ ekipa homeke hone wiaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰pe. Mo hone tulaalaęž‰ some pitaęž‰ mo hone na tulaalaęž‰ some yaapo ipilikaęž‰taęž‰ hando hau pitelepe ekitaęž‰ homeke hau pelepepe.  
\v 16 Mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ tembolotaęž‰ mo pi na miki wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ toopi ti wepia ulaęž‰ alemanu yaapotaęž‰ ekipa hone homeke wiaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰pe. Pa ekipeke. Nikitaęž‰ mo daęž‰ta hao halaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ tembolo da halomaęž‰me. Kodaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ leeke tupaęž‰taęž‰ dupae.  
\q1 Yaka dataęž‰ yaka wandaęž‰hali ameĚ±leĚ± wepulueke. Kutupa iki ameĚ±leĚ± hao halueke. IĚ±taęž‰ ikaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ halueke. Kutupa ikitaęž‰ yaka wandaęž‰hali halimikie leekeme.   
\q1
\v 17 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo Tekehalimaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo wandaęž‰hali minaęž‰paęž‰lao iki ameĚ±leĚ± putupaęž‰ alu pea hapaęž‰peke. Mo haĚ±iĚ±piki haumanu paęž‰taęž‰ nindi pea haluekemaęž‰ taapaęž‰peke. Kutu pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ iki handaęž‰ mulueke.   
\q1
\v 18 IĚ±taęž‰ ikaęž‰ Apaęž‰ halueke. Kutupa ikitaęž‰ yaka wekiwandiki halimikie. Dotaęž‰ Aneke Tekehalimaęž‰ alome laęž‰laęž‰me.   
\c 7  
\p
\v 1 Yaka pukipiki yankeke tonuo do laęž‰ ulaęž‰ pi manutaęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ mo nikaęž‰ loke puki yaapo haĚ±iĚ± peaapeke ekimanu paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ yako pea hamanaęž‰e. Kutupa nikaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ paalaęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ haumaęž‰ otaęž‰ niki yako pea hamanaęž‰e.   
\s1 Polonaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰eki  
\p
\v 2 Ikaęž‰ puki paęž‰taęž‰manu nikaęž‰ da pandaęž‰ wepiapee. Nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hoke hau na polomaęž‰me. Nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ tekipuleke na laomaęž‰me. Kutupa maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ imeke peaake pimanu laa ipikaęž‰ alemanu muluekemaęž‰ na taapomaęž‰me.  
\v 3 IĚ±maęž‰ doeki alo ekitaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ hoke hau pelememe laa maĚ±leke litolo na loaęž‰me. IĚ±maęž‰ ambaęž‰ titinaęž‰ loaęž‰ tupaęž‰ ikitaęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ yole pelemeeki yalotaęž‰ nikaęž‰ temokotaęž‰ hoto paeyao iki ameĚ±leĚ± mandakenaęž‰ halomaęž‰me. Niki pa halomaęž‰ dinaęž‰ make homolomaęž‰ dinaęž‰ make loaęž‰me.  
\v 4 IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ ikitaęž‰ anaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰me hone ulume. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ piteleme haunaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki minolome. Nikaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homolomaęž‰ ekimanu paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ hali au la hataęž‰ honkopu haasaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ tumbu halaęž‰me. IĚ±taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ tumbaa ankou alaęž‰me.  
\v 5 Mo Maęž‰sedonia opolo pomaęž‰ dinaęž‰ maketaęž‰ nikitaęž‰ hoto otaęž‰ na pitumaęž‰me. Kaęž‰ndaęž‰ paeyao manutaęž‰ tumbulu baeyekeme. Maęž‰ndaęž‰ ameĚ±leĚ± ape alaęž‰eki make nikaęž‰ pukimanu paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ paalaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu make pitiaęž‰me.  
\v 6 Pate mo puki hoelaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali honkopu hawao halaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo Taitasi epolo piaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ niki honkopu hawayaęž‰me.  
\v 7 Mo ipiki epolo piaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ homeke niki taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ na homaęž‰ tiayaęž‰pate pa mo ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki honkopu hawaemeeki aęž‰pa la kiaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ make niki taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰ tiayaęž‰me. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± handawee laa we pambelememe laataęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ otaęž‰ hokeeki pumaęž‰me laa kelepeleme ekinaęž‰ make mo IĚ±naęž‰ taĚ±luekemaęž‰ tikitiki yao halemeeki make paeyao aęž‰pa la kiaęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰ ametaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰ tieke otaęž‰ wopu paęž‰laęž‰me.   
\p
\v 8 Mo yaka tapaowaęž‰ tameiyaęž‰maęž‰ iki kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homaeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ laawaęž‰me laa aęž‰taęž‰e pi na alome. Mo tameiyaęž‰maęž‰ iki nate maęž‰ndaęž‰ ninaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homawaęž‰eki handoaęž‰ dinaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homolo puaęž‰me.  
\v 9 Pate ametaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolome. Iki aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰ tiawaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ diaęž‰yaęž‰laęž‰pate pa mo ikaęž‰ homeme kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ haumanu topo peayaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ loaęž‰me. Koto kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ peayaęž‰eki yalo nikanaęž‰maęž‰ iki na hoeyaomaęž‰me.  
\v 10 Pa ekipeke mo Kodaęž‰maęž‰ homo tiaasaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ puki topo peaasaęž‰eki mea ipulu hataęž‰ daęž‰taęž‰monoyeke paęž‰taęž‰laęž‰laęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ hatuku pulaęž‰mee. Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ koto paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± hoeyaasaęž‰ ekie pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ lapeke na yaęž‰laęž‰me. Pate do kenkenaęž‰ hau paęž‰taęž‰ ipulaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki handaęž‰ u halaęž‰me.  
\v 11 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ do ikaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homemeeki paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰eki handaęž‰pe. Titinaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ bu alo hataęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± koto kone ikaęž‰ peleme hoke haumanu tikitiki yamenaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰me. Kutaataęž‰ ikaęž‰ pimi hoke hau manutaęž‰ ametaęž‰ otaęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰lalomaęž‰me laa waluekemaęž‰ hone wopu witeleme ekinaęž‰ make iki epeaalaęž‰maęž‰ handaęž‰pe. Aęž‰paęž‰e. Ametaęž‰ topo wopu pea pimikaęž‰taęž‰me. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo ataęž‰kaęž‰ peaaseke mineke pankaęž‰laęž‰ hau make puki yokaęž‰ miniki hasaęž‰ hau make pea pimikaęž‰taęž‰me. Otaęž‰ alomaęž‰ epeke honemanu witolo hataęž‰ puki wopu wia pimikaęž‰taęž‰me. Kutupataęž‰ hoke hau aĚ±iĚ± koto kone panisi pealuekemaęž‰ tikitiki yao hataęž‰ pimikaęž‰taęž‰me. Koto peleme ekitaęž‰ mo ambaęž‰ putia epolomaęž‰ hau paeyao paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ ikitaęž‰ ataęž‰kaęž‰ na piki wandaęž‰halie laa walaęž‰laęž‰eki handolome.   
\p
\v 12 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ mo tameiyaęž‰ laowaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ mo hoke hau piaęž‰ somenaęž‰ o hoke hau paęž‰laęž‰maęž‰ leaęž‰ somenaęž‰ na laawaęž‰me. Kotoeki na pikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ mo ikanaęž‰maęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homelemeeki iki paęž‰taęž‰ kone peneme yaaluekemaęž‰ puaęž‰me.  
\v 13 Koto ekinaęž‰ yeketaęž‰ nikitaęž‰ honkopu hawaememe. Kotoeki homeke diaęž‰yaęž‰laęž‰pate pa ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Taitasi taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homo tiaemeke handaa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰ wopu homeaęž‰me. Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ kutu piaęž‰eki handolo hataęž‰ niki make taęž‰naęž‰ tieke wopu piaęž‰me.  
\v 14 IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi lawaowaęž‰me. Kutupa ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ na olopuniano lememe. Nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi homeke homeke laa kumaęž‰me. Koto tupaęž‰ konetaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ Taitasi paęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi lawaomaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ekie laa handaęž‰ ulaęž‰me.  
\v 15 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ honkopu hao daeyatia pulaęž‰me. Mo ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ waleaęž‰ ekimanu koto kone opua pimime. Kutupa make ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki paalaęž‰maęž‰ make pututumaęž‰ make homolo hataęž‰ handaęž‰ mimi ekinaęž‰ make loaęž‰me.  
\v 16 IĚ±taęž‰ ikaęž‰naęž‰ ti laapeke yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me hone witolo hataęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰ tieke wopu paęž‰laęž‰me.   
\c 8  
\s1 Ketiso hau pea halaęž‰laęž‰eki  
\p
\v 1 Nikaęž‰ kame tonuo nikaęž‰ honemaęž‰taęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homa tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ mo Maęž‰sedonia siosimanu paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰laęž‰eki ikanaęž‰maęž‰ hone uemenaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 2 Mo wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ mutia peme kaęž‰ndaęž‰ manumaęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ hoke tupaęž‰ la handeaęž‰pate ikaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homeme ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ tieke aneke yaeyeke handaa ikitaęž‰ natehali wandaęž‰hali hataęž‰ kone ikaęž‰ alemanu pa haleme ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ ankulake hau pimime.  
\v 3 IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alo ekitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ haleme ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ halaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ make otaęž‰ hakaęž‰taęž‰pake tupaęž‰ make halememe. Ikaęž‰ hone lombei peake tupaęž‰taęž‰  
\v 4 mo Diudia da kenke paęž‰taęž‰ haleme Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wandaęž‰hali tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ make tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰eki pa peomonope laa niki paęž‰taęž‰ honke tieke lememe.  
\v 5 Kutu pimi haumaęž‰taęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ pinaęž‰ lawee laa hone umaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ ankulao pimime. Titinaęž‰taęž‰ iki kone Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ halememe. Kutupataęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰taęž‰ ikitaęž‰ niki paęž‰taęž‰ make kimime.   
\p
\v 6 Koto ekinaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ do e kini piaęž‰ some Taitasi paęž‰taęž‰ do taęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ piki pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ e ikanaęž‰maęž‰ paeyamenaęž‰yeke tambaęž‰ mu hapeke laa honke lomaęž‰me.  
\v 7 Ikitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ wia halemeeki paeyao paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ hamoko halememe. Ikaęž‰ hone tulaasemeeki paęž‰taęž‰ make pi aleme paęž‰taęž‰ make hone witelemeeki paęž‰taęž‰ make ikaęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± koto kone tambaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ hone witeleme paęž‰taęž‰ make kutupa niki paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homeleme ekimaęž‰ make loaęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ nikaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ do pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ e pokaęž‰laęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ hakaęž‰taęž‰pao mandaneeki pa haloemenaęž‰yeke loaęž‰me   
\p
\v 8 IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ manaęž‰ pimanu maęž‰ndaęž‰ na lo witolome. Pate mo mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± tambaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ hone witelemeeki waloloeki paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ ikaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homeleme ekitaęž‰ ekipape la handuluekemaęž‰ pitolome.  
\v 9 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ nikaęž‰ Tekehali Yesu Ketisonaęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homa tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ hone wilimime. Ipikitaęž‰ hamoko tieke hayekepate iki tambaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ yeke ipikitaęž‰ nate hali au leekeme. Kototaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ natehali au leeke ekimaęž‰ iki hamoko hawaluekemaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰me.   
\p
\v 10 Ya honemaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande paeyaęž‰ bapinaęž‰ kini pimi ekitaęž‰ ame do paeyaasotaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me hone witolome. Tambaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ homeke diaęž‰yaęž‰laęž‰pate pa puluekemaęž‰ hone witelemeeki make ikitaęž‰ titinaęž‰ ambaęž‰laęž‰e.  
\v 11 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ ame tiao ikaęž‰ kini pimieki aĚ±iĚ± paeyaapee. Mo taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ dupa pulumeke laa laęž‰ wimi tupaęž‰ kone paeyaaluekemaęž‰ make aĚ±iĚ± paeyaalumeke laa hone wipee. Kutupa make ame do wia halemeeki pitaęž‰ pipee.  
\v 12 Ikitaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolo aĚ±iĚ± haluekemaęž‰ hone wimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo ikaęž‰ pa haluekemaęž‰ wia haleme aletaęž‰ milieke. Pate mo na wia haleme alenaęž‰ diaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 13-14 Mandane wandaęž‰hali ikaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰manu yapaęž‰ peaaso hataęž‰ ikitaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homaasome laa na loaęž‰pate pa ametaęž‰ ikitaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ wopu wia halemeke handaa mo diaęž‰yaęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰hali tambaęž‰ mimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ anaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰me. Kutupa nate maęž‰ndaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ iki diaęž‰yaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ anekemaęž‰ wia haemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ iki make tambaęž‰ milieke. Dupitaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ telipunaęž‰taęž‰ anaęž‰ sikinaęž‰ tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 15 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo Baibolomaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo aneke hapu mombeleaęž‰ sometaęž‰ lombeipiki tupaęž‰ na wia hayaęž‰me. Kutupa mo hosiki siki mombeleaęž‰ sometaęž‰ otaęž‰ diaęž‰yaęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ na wia hayaęž‰me laęž‰laęž‰me.   
\s1 Taitasi pitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ yankeke tonu  
\p
\v 16 Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ iki tambaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ hone wopu ulumaęž‰ tupaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ Taitasi mea hone wopu utialaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ keiyae alomaęž‰me.  
\v 17 Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ polenaęž‰e lomaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ opua taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homeaęž‰me. Koto lomaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ homeke diaęž‰yaęž‰laęž‰pate ipikaęž‰ honemaęž‰ kone iki paęž‰taęž‰ tambaęž‰ muluaęž‰ ipulueke hone wiaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ lomaęž‰me.  
\v 18 Ipiki yaapotaęž‰ mo kame maęž‰ndaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ siosi paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ mo pi seliapo walaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ otaęž‰ epeke halie lo haleme kame tapaasomaęž‰me.  
\v 19 Kutupa make ipikitaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ do pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ e pokotia pominolomaęž‰ ale paęž‰taęž‰ mandakenaęž‰ pomiomono yeke mo siosi manumaęž‰ maĚ±leke lilaęž‰me. Do e pokolomaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ teketaęž‰ mo Tekehalinaęž‰ paĚ±aĚ±naęž‰ make mo nikitaęž‰ tambaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ hone wopu witolomaęž‰me laa waluekemaęž‰ pitolomaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 20 Nikitaęž‰ do epeke pa kitaęž‰laęž‰eki mea pominolomaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ mandane wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ hambilikimaęž‰ hambilikimaęž‰ pea la la peaamaęž‰naęž‰yeke leke wia hataęž‰ pitolomaęž‰me.  
\v 21 Nikaęž‰ hone homeke homeketaęž‰ otaęž‰ tikitiki hau homeke puluekemaęž‰ hone witolomaęž‰me. Otaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ homeke diaęž‰yaęž‰laęž‰pate pa kenke wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ make loaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 22 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ mo haliweki ameĚ±leĚ± nikaęž‰ kame taa tapaasomaęž‰ handaęž‰e. Nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ hoto paeyao ipiki la handomaęž‰me. Pate ipikitaęž‰ hoto paeyao tambaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ hone wopu ulaęž‰eki handaęž‰ ulumaęž‰me. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ambaęž‰taęž‰ iki tambaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ hone wiaęž‰pate pa ametaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaalaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± tambaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ hone wopu wia halaęž‰me.  
\v 23 Taitasitaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ yaka taęž‰maęž‰ni hataęž‰ iki tambaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ IĚ± yaapo e poko halaęž‰me. Kutupa mo ipiki ameĚ±leĚ± pulaęž‰ mandane kame tonutaęž‰ do siosi manunaęž‰ bikinaęž‰ ipulaęž‰ hataęž‰taęž‰ Ketisonaęž‰ biki daeyaenaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰ tapakee.  
\v 24  Ikaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ mo tapake paęž‰taęž‰ walaęž‰paęž‰peke. Pa ekipeke mo siosi manumaęž‰ hone witolotaęž‰ mo nikanaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi laomaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰me laa hone winaęž‰ loaęž‰me.   
\c 9  
\s1 Ketiso yankeke tonu tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰eki  
\p
\v 1 Mo Diudia da kenke paęž‰taęž‰ haleme Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ tapaalaęž‰ tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ do laaso tameiyaęž‰ tapapeketaęž‰ ti na paęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 2 Pa ekipeke ikanaęž‰maęž‰ tambaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ hone wopu wilimi ekitaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ hone ulume. Kutupa ikaęž‰ piteleme ekitaęž‰ mo Maęž‰sedonia wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ pi la waloaęž‰me. Mo wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ alotaęž‰ Mo Akaya haleme kame tonumaęž‰taęž‰ mo paeyaęž‰ bapinaęž‰ kini pea tambaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ tikitiki yao halememe laa loaęž‰me. Ikaęž‰ puluekemaęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± hone wilimi ekimaęž‰taęž‰ wopunaęž‰ hone u tialememe.  
\v 3 Koto ekinaęž‰ ametaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ do kamemanu tapaasome. Pa ekipeke mo nikanaęž‰maęž‰ do haunaęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi laomaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ pa hameke pi lomaęž‰me hone wiaamaęž‰naęž‰ loaęž‰me. Pate IĚ±maęž‰ ambaęž‰ loaęž‰ tupaęž‰taęž‰ ikitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰eki manumaęž‰ tikitiki yao halememe loaęž‰me.  
\v 4 Pate mo Maęž‰sedonia wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ IĚ± ameĚ±leĚ± ipulu iki tikitiki yao na halemeeki handaęž‰ wimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ nikitaęž‰ otaęž‰ pulu pimime laa ekipiki yaalaęž‰maęž‰ homulumaęž‰pe. Ikaęž‰ yaalaęž‰ pulu paęž‰laęž‰eki make loaęž‰me.  
\v 5 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ yaka honemaęž‰taęž‰ do kame tonumaęž‰ ambaęž‰la kinki pulu ipulu mo ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ambaęž‰ laęž‰ wimi pa hameke halaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ tikitiki yamenaęž‰ tapaowaęž‰me. Kutupa IĚ± opolo epoaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ tikitiki yao wiemenaęž‰ loaęž‰me. Kutu pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ haleleme ekitaęž‰ mo ikaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ kone halelememe laa walieke. Maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ piaęž‰paęž‰peke laęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ diaęž‰me loaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 6 Hone wipee. Mo hande wae alemanu wopu na nokaęž‰paęž‰laęž‰ halimaęž‰taęž‰ napeke hosiki siki mu halaęž‰pate mo wae ale aneke hapu nokaęž‰paęž‰laęž‰ halimaęž‰taęž‰ napeke tieke mu halaęž‰me.  
\v 7 Koto ekinaęž‰ iki homeke homekemaęž‰ dupiki halueke laa leme tupaęž‰ halaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me. Haluekemaęž‰ hosiki kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ o do e pokaęž‰laęž‰eki minaęž‰paęž‰lapeke na yaęž‰laęž‰me laa alo hataęž‰ diaęž‰me Pa ekipeke Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ halaęž‰laęž‰ some paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 8 Kutupa Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ diaęž‰yaęž‰ tupaęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ hakaęž‰taęž‰pao wopu kuluekemaęž‰ aneke hali halaęž‰me. Pa ekipeke iki diaęž‰yaęž‰laęž‰ ale anaęž‰naęž‰ wia hamenaęž‰yeke make mo mandane epeke haumanu paęž‰taęž‰laęž‰laęž‰eki otaęž‰ hakaęž‰taęž‰pao wia hamenaęž‰yeke make loaęž‰me.  
\v 9 Kototaęž‰ mo Baibolomaęž‰ alotaęž‰  
\q1 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pa hameke halaęž‰laęž‰ alemanu mo diaęž‰yaęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰hali minaęž‰yeke sasape peaęž‰tiki pu halaęž‰me.  
\q1 Ipikaęž‰ tikitiki pitaęž‰laęž‰ hautaęž‰ na paeyeke pa u halieke laa laęž‰laęž‰me.   
\p
\v 10 Kutupa mo nokaęž‰paęž‰laęž‰ halinaęž‰ wae ale halo halaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo napeke ne make halo halaęž‰me. Koto Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ hoto paeyao mo ikaęž‰ diaęž‰yaęž‰laęž‰ wae ale hakaęž‰taęž‰pao ku hataęž‰ ikaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ pa haleme haunaęž‰ openaęž‰ laa napeke tieke aęž‰enaęž‰ laęž‰lieke.   
\p
\v 11 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ ikaęž‰ ale mandaneeki pa halo hamenaęž‰yeke iki hamoko hawalieke. Kutu pimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo ikaęž‰ pa halelemeeki niki paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ minolo hataęž‰ wandaęž‰hali wopumaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ keiyae laęž‰limikie.  
\v 12 Do ikanaęž‰maęž‰ pokeleme emaęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ diaęž‰yaęž‰laęž‰eki homeke na epeaasaęž‰pate pa Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ keiyae tieke alaęž‰ pi wopu lenaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰me  
\v 13 Kutupa do ikaęž‰ pokeleme emaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ epeke hau peneme yaaso hataęž‰ paeyaomaęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Ketisonaęž‰ Pi Seliapo oto paęž‰taęž‰ haleme ekinaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ biki yeiyaęž‰ lalimikie. Mo ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ ale mandaneeki pa halo halemeeki iki ameĚ±leĚ± telipa make paeyao ameĚ±leĚ± putupeleme ekinaęž‰ loaęž‰me.  
\v 14 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki tiekemaęž‰ ikinaęž‰ yeni peaalimikie. Pa ekipeke mo Kodaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ anekemaęž‰ hakaęž‰taęž‰pake aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki kaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ loaęž‰me.  
\v 15 Niki paeyaomaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ otaęž‰ au lapeke na yeke pa kitaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ keiyae lomanaęž‰e.   
\c 10  
\s1 Polomaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ enaęž‰ mape liekeeki  
\p
\v 1 IĚ±taęž‰ Polomaęž‰ ya kone iki paęž‰taęž‰ honke alome. IĚ±taęž‰ hande iki ameĚ±leĚ± halo dinaęž‰taęž‰ homu pea dete polopate iki minaęž‰paęž‰lao papate halo dinaęž‰taęž‰ tanda polaęž‰me lo halaęž‰maęž‰ somemaęž‰ loaęž‰me. Ketisonaęž‰ homu tolomaęž‰ litaęž‰laęž‰eki pitaęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ puki halaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ iki honke alotaęž‰  
\v 2 IĚ± epoaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ tanda piono na sutiaamenaęž‰ yeke loaęž‰me. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ mo nikanaęž‰maęž‰ kenkenaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ hau paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ pitolomaęž‰me laa aleme tapake paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ tanda piaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me laa hone ulume.  
\v 3 Nikitaęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ otaęž‰ halomaęž‰pate nikitaęž‰ kenkenaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ hau paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ na pitolomaęž‰me.  
\v 4 Mo nikanaęž‰maęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ pitolo hataęž‰ wia halomaęž‰ kolepe aęž‰ndeli manutaęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ diaęž‰yaęž‰laęž‰me. Pate mo hande honkopu hake aęž‰ndaęž‰ pape hoeyao halomaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wele wopupiki kolepe aęž‰ndelimaęž‰ pu halomaęž‰me. Nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ makeaaso ape alaęž‰ ekimanu hoeyao halomaęž‰me.  
\v 5 Mo Kodaęž‰ hone wiaapaęž‰naęž‰ saęž‰saęž‰ puluekemaęž‰ mea tiao pu halemeeki paeyao nikanaęž‰maęž‰ mea lopao halomaęž‰me. Nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ honemanu paeyao minaataęž‰ Ketisonaęž‰ pi opua homu pinaęž‰ lo halomaęž‰me.  
\v 6 Kutupa ikanaęž‰maęž‰ pi opua oto paęž‰taęž‰ halimieki handaęž‰ wia paeyaalimi dinaęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo pi opua oto paęž‰taęž‰ na hao halimieki panisi pealuekemaęž‰ nikitaęž‰ tikitiki yao halumeke.   
\p
\v 7 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo alaęž‰taęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰naęž‰ hamaęž‰ naneeki handelememe. Iki ameĚ±leĚ± maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ Ketiso paęž‰taęž‰ tunaalome alaęž‰ some halaęž‰pe. Kotaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hau pitaęž‰laęž‰eki kone pa hone winaęž‰e. Pa ekipeke ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ kone niki make Ketiso paęž‰taęž‰ tunaalomaęž‰me.  
\v 8 Kotaęž‰ mo Tekehalimaęž‰ niki kaęž‰laęž‰ handeteke halaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ pi tieke lawaęž‰pate IĚ±taęž‰ yaalaęž‰ na paęž‰laęž‰me. Iki na hoeyake mea daeyamono kaęž‰laęž‰ handeteke halaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ loaęž‰me.  
\v 9 Mo yaka tameiyaęž‰ manumaęž‰taęž‰ iki paalaęž‰ tiaasaęž‰eki handoemenaęž‰ hone na ulume.  
\v 10 Maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±naęž‰ do laęž‰lieke. Polonaęž‰ tameiyaęž‰ manutaęž‰ tanda pea honkopu halaęž‰pate pa mo ipikaęž‰ loke piti niki ameĚ±leĚ± halaęž‰ dinaęž‰taęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ dete pea ipikaęž‰ pi manutaęž‰ teke na ulaęž‰me laa lelieke.  
\v 11 Koto alaęž‰ somemaęž‰taęž‰ dupa hone wiaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me. Mo nikitaęž‰ papate hataęž‰ tameiyaęž‰naęž‰ laasomaęž‰eki pitaęž‰ mo iki ameĚ±leĚ± hataęž‰ pulu polomaęž‰eki yaapo paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ eki maęž‰ndaęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ na paęž‰laęž‰me hone wiaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me.   
\p
\v 12 Otaęž‰ yaęž‰laęž‰pate nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo niki dupolomaęž‰me o nikaęž‰ kone mo ikitaęž‰ manda halomaęž‰me laa lo haleme tapake paęž‰taęž‰ na yolaęž‰ pambolomaęž‰taęž‰ pa iki otaęž‰ hoke anaęž‰ na piki haliwekie. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ halemeeki tombo muluekemaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ tombo minaęž‰laęž‰ ale wepia maka mea handolo hataęž‰ dupiki somee laa lo halememe. Kutu pu halemepate  
\v 13 nikanaęž‰maęž‰ nikaęž‰ hakoko litolomaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ tombo ulaęž‰eki na ankulalumeke. Mo Kodaęž‰maęž‰ nikaęž‰ e tikitiki yaalaęž‰ tombo taapu halieke. Do ekitaęž‰ mo iki ameĚ±leĚ± nikanaęž‰maęž‰ pokolomaęž‰ e make apaęž‰taasaęž‰me.  
\v 14 Kutupa ikitaęž‰ koto tombo taapu haleme ekinaęž‰taęž‰ nikitaęž‰ koto tombo minaęž‰paęž‰lao mopate leke na pomaęž‰me. Mo iki paęž‰taęž‰ hande Ketisonaęž‰ Pi Seliapo mea epomaęž‰ dinaęž‰ loaęž‰me.  
\v 15 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰maęž‰ nikaęž‰ tombo wia yekeeki ankulao mopate leke pokeme tapakenaęž‰ enaęž‰ hakoko na litolomaęž‰me. Kotoeki na pikitaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ hone witolomaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone tulaaseme ekitaęž‰ daetolo hataęž‰ iki ameĚ±leĚ± e wopu pokuluekemaęž‰ hone wopu witolomaęž‰me. Koto ekitaęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰maęž‰ laęž‰ ulaęž‰ tombo paęž‰taęž‰ hoto paeyao hataęž‰ pokomono loaęž‰me.  
\v 16 Kutu paataęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo Pi Seliapotaęž‰ mo papate halaęž‰ tutu maęž‰ndaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ walolo hataęž‰ mo hali maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ ambaęž‰ pokeaęž‰ enaęž‰ kenke paęž‰taęž‰ hakoko na liomono yeke loaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 17 Pate mo Baibolomaęž‰ alotaęž‰ Maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ pi latia pomulueke hone wiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ otaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ pi latia pomuaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me laęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 18 Maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ epeke halie hone witaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ epeke hali diaęž‰yaęž‰laęž‰pate pa mo Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ epeke halie leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto sometaęž‰ otaęž‰ epeke hali halaęž‰me.   
\c 11  
\s1 Polo pitaęž‰ makeaaso aposolo haliweki  
\p
\v 1 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ hosiki hone wopu na wiki hake nono pimanu lono aĚ±iĚ± na kiake waleke siki kipe laa honke alome.  
\v 2 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ hone wopu witolo leke wia halaęž‰ tupaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ make iki paęž‰taęž‰ homeke hone wopu witolo hataęž‰ leke wia halome. Ikitaęž‰ mo hande maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ hakopu na tunkuliki pa halaęž‰ moputali wandikimaęž‰ handelememe. Kutupa IĚ±maęž‰ koto wandikitaęž‰ otaęž‰ hali homeke Ketisomaęž‰ kone minaęž‰ laa ambaęž‰ laęž‰ uaęž‰me.  
\v 3 Ikaęž‰ hone manutaęž‰ hoeyaasaęž‰eki manumaęž‰ mea bepolao ikaęž‰ otaęž‰ Ketiso paęž‰taęž‰ homeke alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ na taĚ±leke pukimaęž‰ homelemeeki hoki walimikie laataęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ paalaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰me. Mo hande ketonaęž‰ hone wopu lenkene piki yayapiki pimaęž‰ hande Ipaęž‰ makeaeyeke tupaęž‰ kone pilieke laa loaęž‰me.  
\v 4 Pa ekipeke ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ aęž‰pa mo Yesu maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ walaęž‰laęž‰ pitaęž‰ pa taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaa opu halememe. Mo nikanaęž‰maęž‰ walomaęž‰ Yesunaęž‰ diaęž‰me. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mimi sipitidi pitaęž‰ pi seliapo yaapotaęž‰ otaęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰me. Mo hande nikanaęž‰maęž‰ mea epomaęž‰ Sipitidi pitaęž‰ Pi Seliapo yaapo otaęž‰ diaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 5 IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ koto ikaęž‰ mea aęž‰meiyaaseme aposolo aleme haliweki otaęž‰ hosiki siki make oto paęž‰taęž‰ halome hone na ulume.  
\v 6 IĚ±taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ yaka pi alo paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ meĚ±iĚ±meĚ±iĚ± lialopate pa mo hone witoloeki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ diaęž‰me hone witolome. Nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ hau paeyao paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ koto ekitaęž‰ peneme yatiki pu halomaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 7 IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ mo hande Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Pi Seliapo waloaęž‰ dinaęž‰taęž‰ ikitaęž‰ otaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰siki make yenki kipe pi na loaęž‰me. Iki otaęž‰ aneke wandaęž‰hali au laluekemaęž‰ yeke IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ ya kone homu pea lu minaęž‰niaowaęž‰me. Kototaęž‰ ataęž‰kaęž‰ piki hau puaęž‰pe.  
\v 8 IĚ±maęž‰ iki tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ e pokoaęž‰ dinaęž‰taęž‰ mandane siosi manumaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ yenki kimime. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ iki tambaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰yeke mo wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ mani pake neke nono puaęž‰me.  
\v 9 Kutupa iki ameĚ±leĚ± haowaęž‰ natenaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± mani diaęž‰yeketaęž‰ IĚ± tambaęž‰ mipe laa iki paęž‰taęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ peaapeke honke na loaęž‰me. Pa ekipeke mo Maęž‰sedonia nanemaęž‰ epeme kame tonumaęž‰ IĚ± diaęž‰yaęž‰laęž‰ ale paeyao aneke mea aęž‰paememe. Ambaęž‰ puaęž‰ tupaęž‰ wetepe ninaęž‰ make IĚ±taęž‰ iki kaęž‰ndaęž‰ homaaluekemaęž‰ na taapulueke.  
\v 10 Ketisonaęž‰ otaęž‰ pi IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ pilaęž‰eki yalotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ do yaka hakoko litolo pitaęž‰ otaęž‰ koto Akaya kenke paeyao paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ na palueke laa pi laęž‰ witolome.  
\v 11 IĚ±maęž‰ do alo ekitaęž‰ iki pukimaęž‰ na homolome laa alope. Diaęž‰me. IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homolo ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ hone ulaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 12 IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ ame do pitolo ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ pa pitolo ombu halueke. Pa ekipeke mo koto mandane aposoloe lo haleme haliwekimaęž‰ hakoko litolo hataęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ pokeme tupaęž‰ kone pokolomaęž‰me alemeeki saęž‰saęž‰ puluekemaęž‰ loaęž‰me.  
\v 13 Koto haliwekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ aposolo haliweki diaęž‰me. Ikitaęž‰ makeaaso aposolo haliweki hataęž‰ ikaęž‰ pokeleme enaęž‰ yayapiki pi laataęž‰ ikitaęž‰ Ketisonaęž‰ otaęž‰ aposolo haliweki leke au lo halememe.  
\v 14 Kotaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰maęž‰ hone wopu wiaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me. Pa ekipeke Sadanimaęž‰ kone ipikitaęž‰ mo paĚ±aĚ±piki enisolomaęž‰ handeke nono pu hapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 15 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pa hameke e pokaasaęž‰ haliwekimaęž‰ iki make otaęž‰ tikitiki piki haunaęž‰ e pokaasaęž‰ haliweki hataęž‰ au lemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ kotoeki hau tieke diaęž‰me. Paetolo nate ninaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ pimi haumaęž‰ walaęž‰laęž‰ yenki kone milimikie.   
\s1 Polotaęž‰ aposolo hataęž‰ mieke tandamanu  
\p
\v 16 IĚ±maęž‰ pa yaapo peao dupa alome. Maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ hone na wiki halie hone wiaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me. Pate ikanaęž‰maęž‰ koto hone wimikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰me. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ hosiki siki haunaęž‰ hakoko liono IĚ±taęž‰ hone na wiki hali leke handaęž‰ mipee.  
\v 17 Kotaęž‰ ame IĚ±maęž‰ do alo ekitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ lono lolo pi diaęž‰me. Dupiki hakoko litolo ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰e mo hone na wiki somemaęž‰ alaęž‰ tupaęž‰ alome.  
\v 18 Kutu paęž‰laęž‰pate kenke haunaęž‰ hakoko liteleme wandaęž‰hali wopu halemeeki yalotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ make homeke hau pulueke.  
\v 19 Ikitaęž‰ lombei peao hone wopu wilimieki yalotaęž‰ mo hone na wiki haliwekitaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homa handaęž‰ mu halememe.  
\v 20 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo iki dupi dupi lo haleme haliweki make o iki teke puleke lao haleme haliweki make o iki honaęž‰maĚ±oĚ± haleme o iki handaęž‰niao haleme o iki kadapo ku haleme haliweki paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ ikaęž‰ pi opu halememe.  
\v 21 Nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ kutupiki haumanu puluekemaęž‰ dodaęž‰pikinaęž‰ na pumaęž‰taęž‰ laa loluekemaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ yaalaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰me.  
\p Pate maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰naęž‰ honkopu hao hakoko lulueke hone wiaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ make hone na wiki some leke mandake tupaęž‰ loluekemaęž‰ anaęž‰naęž‰ honkopu hao peaęž‰peke yaęž‰lieke.  
\v 22 Ikitaęž‰ Hibulu yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰pe kotaęž‰ IĚ± make lataa. Ikitaęž‰ Isulai yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰pe kotaęž‰ IĚ± make lataa. Ikitaęž‰ Eipolohaęž‰maęž‰naęž‰ tapake yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰pe kotaęž‰ IĚ± make lataa.  
\v 23 Ikitaęž‰ Ketisonaęž‰ e pokaaseme haliweki yaęž‰kaęž‰taęž‰pe kotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ you hoke halimaęž‰ leke nono pitolopate IĚ±taęž‰ e pokaaso hali hataęž‰ iki lombei peaalome. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ lombei peaaso hataęž‰ oto honkopu hao e wopu pokolome. IĚ±taęž‰ dipula da paęž‰taęž‰manu otaęž‰ lombei piki hoto eleke eleke mea pitaalememe. IĚ±taęž‰ otaęž‰ lombei peake tupaęž‰ dopitamaęž‰ yombelememe. Kutupa IĚ±taęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki tombonaęž‰ teke paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ lombei piki natemanu meaęž‰tiki polome.  
\v 24 Mo Diu tapakemaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ hoto yunki hataęž‰naęž‰ minaataęž‰ pumaęž‰ hoto 39 peao IĚ± yombimime.  
\v 25 Kutupa hoto tepotaęž‰ mo Lomaęž‰ haliwekimaęž‰ dopitamaęž‰ IĚ± yombimime. Kutupa hoto homeketaęž‰ toopimaęž‰ IĚ± limime. IĚ±taęž‰ hoto tepotaęž‰ mo sisima kawasotaęž‰ toopinaęž‰ tulaaso yambolo hoeyaęž‰tiki puaęž‰me. Kutupa hoto maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ nate homekenaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± petelenaęž‰ oni ikali manda pomuaęž‰me.  
\v 26 Yaka wopu pomuaęž‰tiki pu haowaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ manutaęž‰ IĚ± lia homaaluekemaęž‰ mo ikali tieke teaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ teke paęž‰taęž‰ epeaęž‰ make mo pake nalaęž‰ haliwekimaęž‰ make teke paęž‰taęž‰ haememe. Mo Diu yankeke tonu pitaęž‰ Diendaili tapake yaapomaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± hoeyaaluekemaęž‰ hone wimime. Mo daonimanu paęž‰taęž‰ make hapu hayeke alemanu paęž‰taęž‰ make dawala tieke manunaęž‰ make makeaaso yankeke tonu paęž‰taęž‰ make otaęž‰ IĚ± hoeyaapeke alemanu teke paęž‰taęž‰ hatiki pu haowaęž‰me.  
\v 27 Kutupa nate mandaneeki manunaęž‰taęž‰ honkopu paenaęž‰ kone e wopu pokoaęž‰me. Hoto eleke eleke timbaęž‰ nanetaęž‰ e pokaaluekemaęž‰ u na poluaęž‰me. Nate maęž‰ndaęž‰ ninaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ teaęž‰maęž‰ make ikali naęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ make homoaęž‰me. IĚ±taęž‰ nate maęž‰ndaęž‰ ninaęž‰taęž‰ ne da dau wopu diaęž‰yalo hataęž‰ pa haowaęž‰me.  
\v 28 Kutupa mandane haumanu winaęž‰ konetaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ hoto paeyaotaęž‰ mo siosi paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ hone uluekemaęž‰ IĚ± otaęž‰ tumbaalaęž‰me.  
\v 29 Maęž‰ndaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ damako piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± make homeke tupaęž‰ damako pu halome. Maęž‰ndaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ hoke hau paęž‰taęž‰ mea lopaeyaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ ya puki paęž‰taęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homolome.   
\p
\v 30 IĚ±maęž‰ hakoko liaęž‰peke yaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ mo IĚ± damako pitoloeki walaęž‰laęž‰ ale manunaęž‰ hakoko lionoe.  
\v 31 Kodaęž‰ mo Tekehali Yesu Ketisonaęž‰ Atekemaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ yayapiki pi na alome laa hone witaęž‰laęž‰me. Ipikaęž‰ bikitaęž‰ hoto paeyao mea aęž‰meiyamanaęž‰e.  
\v 32 IĚ±taęž‰ mo Damasikasi daoni paęž‰taęž‰ haowaęž‰ dinaęž‰taęž‰ mo kini Aletasi oto paęž‰taęž‰ hayaęž‰ kapomani halimaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± mininaęž‰ alo hataęž‰ mo daoni potaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰manu haliweki handeteke hao yapenaęž‰ leaęž‰me.  
\v 33 Pate IĚ±taęž‰ mo daoni pape teaęž‰naęž‰ lombaemeke seto kaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ windo paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ basekede nunaęž‰ pitaęž‰paleke lopaniao ipikaęž‰ kiki paęž‰taęž‰ kaęž‰laęž‰paęž‰taęž‰ pao pindipa poaęž‰me.   
\c 12  
\s1 Polonaęž‰ upamaęž‰ leke waleaęž‰ ekimanu handeekeeki  
\p
\v 1 IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ do hautaęž‰ otaęž‰ teke maęž‰ndaęž‰ na ulaęž‰pate kone otaęž‰ hakoko pa liaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me. IĚ±maęž‰ mo Tekehalimaęž‰ kiaęž‰ pa upamaęž‰ leke handaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu pitaęž‰ peneme yao waleaęž‰ ekimanu yaaponaęž‰ pimanu ame lolueke.  
\v 2 IĚ±maęž‰ hone ulutaęž‰ ambaęž‰ paeyaęž‰ bapi 14 haowaęž‰ dinaęž‰taęž‰ Ketiso hali maęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ oli otaęž‰ manda halaęž‰ hepeni nane paęž‰taęž‰laęž‰ mea peaęž‰eki hone ulume. Do ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ piaęž‰pe o pa upamaęž‰ leke handeaęž‰pe laa IĚ± hone na ulupate Kodaęž‰maęž‰ homeke hone ulaęž‰me.  
\v 3-4 IĚ±maęž‰ yaapo peao paa alome. Koto halitaęž‰ oli Paęž‰taęž‰daisi nane paęž‰taęž‰laęž‰ mea peaęž‰me. Paa alome. Koto hautaęž‰ otaęž‰ piaęž‰me laa make pa upamaęž‰ handeke nono piaęž‰pe laa Kodaęž‰maęž‰ homeke hone ulaęž‰me. Kutupa koto paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ pimaęž‰ lapeke na yaęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu opiaęž‰me. Mo kenke halinaęž‰ kake hambilikimaęž‰ na layeke ekimanu loaęž‰me.  
\v 5 Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ mo halinaęž‰ pi lawalueke. Pate pa yaka kone yaka pi na lalueke. Kutu pulu paęž‰laęž‰pate mo IĚ± damako piki hali haloeki walaęž‰laęž‰eki homeke pi lalueke.   
\p
\v 6 IĚ±maęž‰ pi lalueke hone uaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ hone na wiki some na halueke. Pa ekipeke. Koto pitaęž‰ otaęž‰ pi homeke lolueke. Pate pi na lalueke. Kutupa maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ yaka pokoaęž‰ emanu handolotaęž‰ yaka waloaęž‰ pimanu opitolo hataęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ dupiki somee laa leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰pate pa maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ anemone hone witaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ IĚ± kipaęž‰laęž‰me.   
\s1 Polonaęž‰ lokenaęž‰ mieke tanda  
\p
\v 7 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ peneme yao otaęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ piki epeke haumanu waleaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ wopu handoaęž‰me. Koto handoaęž‰eki manumaęž‰ IĚ± manda meaamaęž‰naęž‰ mo ya loke paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ tanda tieke paęž‰laęž‰eki maęž‰ndaęž‰ kiaęž‰me. Mo ekimaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ hakoko liaamaęž‰naęž‰ yeke Sadanimaęž‰ IĚ± yombinaęž‰ epenaęž‰ leaęž‰me.  
\v 8 Doeki mea bae laa lotaęž‰ pitolo hataęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ hoto teponaęž‰ Tekehali paęž‰taęž‰ yeni puaęž‰pate  
\v 9 ipikaęž‰ hombo peayaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ dupa leaęž‰me. Yaka aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homa tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ anaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰me. Pa ekipeke neke damako pele dinaęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ yaka welenaęž‰ otaęž‰ lombei pea tieke ulaęž‰me leaęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ mo yaka damako paęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu paęž‰taęž‰ hakoko luluekemaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰ wopu paęž‰laęž‰me. Pa ekipeke mo Ketisonaęž‰ handeteke halaęž‰ welemaęž‰ IĚ± handeteke halaęž‰eki handuluekemaęž‰ loaęž‰me.  
\v 10 Koto ekinaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ Ketisonaęž‰eki peaaso mo damako paęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ make tetopiki pimaęž‰ make kaęž‰ndaęž‰piki ekimaęž‰ make aęž‰ndaęž‰ litaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ make mamatalaęž‰ ekimaęž‰ make IĚ±taęž‰ pa taęž‰naęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰me. Pa ekipeke IĚ±taęž‰ damako polo dinaęž‰taęž‰ honkopu hao halome.   
\s1 Polomaęž‰ Kotindi tapake hone wotu wiekeeki  
\p
\v 11 IĚ±taęž‰ hone na wiki halimaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰eki leke pitolopate ikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ kutu pono lelememe. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homelemeeki IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ peneme yao walaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me. IĚ±taęž‰ biki na wiki hali yanaęž‰ kone mo ikaęž‰ leleme taęž‰taęž‰piki aposolo haliweki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ hau homekesiki kone oto paęž‰taęž‰ na halome.  
\v 12 Mo hande na handeke haumanu make taęž‰taęž‰piki haumanu make iki tukikinaęž‰ peneme yaasotaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ otaęž‰ aposolo hali walaęž‰laęž‰me. Kutupiki haumanu puaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ homumaęž‰ puaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ loaęž‰me.  
\v 13 Mo mandane siosi paęž‰taęž‰ tambaęž‰ muaęž‰ tupaęž‰taęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ ekipiki homeke hau aęž‰ndaęž‰ na puaęž‰pe. Hau homeketaęž‰ pa ikaęž‰ manimaęž‰ IĚ± tambaęž‰ muemenaęž‰ laa kaęž‰ndaęž‰ na peaowaęž‰me. Aęž‰taęž‰e. Do IĚ±maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ mandake hau na puaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ pa paeyawapee.   
\p
\v 14 Ametaęž‰ hoto tepo peao iki handolo ipuluekemaęž‰ tikitiki yaasopate iki paęž‰taęž‰ honke alaęž‰ ekimanu maęž‰ndaęž‰ na pulueke. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ manimanu hone na paęž‰laęž‰pate otaęž‰ iki homeke yaka yankeke hamenaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰me. Pa ekipeke weki wandikimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ apaęž‰ amaęž‰naęž‰ diaęž‰yaęž‰laęž‰ alemanu na anaęž‰ laalo paęž‰laęž‰pate apaęž‰ amaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ weki wandikinaęž‰ diaęž‰yaęž‰laęž‰ ale anaęž‰ lawaapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 15 Koto ekinaęž‰ yaka taęž‰naęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ iki tambaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ yeketaęž‰ yaka wia halo ale paeyao make IĚ± kone make pa baalueke laataęž‰ IĚ± hone wopu paęž‰laęž‰me. IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ iki pukimaęž‰ wopu homolo ekinaęž‰ yeke ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ hosikimaęž‰ kone puki kilimikipe.   
\p
\v 16 IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ iki kaęž‰ndaęž‰ na peaowaęž‰me laataęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰e lelimikie. Pate maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ makeaaso hataęž‰ ikitaęž‰ yayapiki pi manumaęž‰ tameaęž‰me laa lelieke.  
\v 17 Pate ekipa yakaęž‰taęž‰ mo IĚ±maęž‰ pi mea epenaęž‰ tapaowaęž‰ haliweki paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ iki teke puleke lawaęž‰pe.  
\v 18 IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ Taitasi pue laa honke laataęž‰ ipiki ameĚ±leĚ± mo hande Ketiso kame maęž‰ndaęž‰ make tapaowaęž‰me. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ Taitasimaęž‰ iki teke puleke laeyaęž‰me lelimipe. Dikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ homeke hau teke peaataęž‰ otaęž‰ homeke tupaęž‰ popeke paęž‰laęž‰ haumanu na pupaęž‰pe.   
\p
\v 19 Mataęž‰laęž‰me. Hoto paeyaotaęž‰ ikaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ nikaęž‰ kone tambaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ pitolomaęž‰me hone witolo pitelememe. Diaęž‰me. Nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ hataęž‰ Ketisomaęž‰ niki pi lomono lolo paęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ alomaęž‰me. Kutupa nikaęž‰ puki piki yankeke tonuo nikanaęž‰maęž‰ pitolomaęž‰ hau paeyaotaęž‰ iki tambaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ pitolomaęž‰me.  
\v 20 IĚ± koto paęž‰taęž‰ opolo epoaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ikitaęž‰ dupiki wandaęž‰hali aęž‰pa handulueke hone wia ipuluaęž‰pate pa ikitaęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰piki wandaęž‰hali handulueke laa IĚ±taęž‰ paalaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰me. Kutupa make ikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ dupiki some handulumeke hone wilimipate IĚ±taęž‰ pa taęž‰taęž‰ piki some handilimikie. IĚ± paalaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ iki tukiki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ ape alaęž‰ haumanu make ne tunkulaęž‰laęž‰ haumanu make mineke tieke pankaęž‰laęž‰ haumanu make pasaęž‰tei pitaęž‰laęž‰ haumanu make yaalaęž‰ peake haumanu make la la piki pimanu make mandaęž‰ meaasaęž‰ haumanu make mamataasaęž‰ haumanu make paeyao handaęž‰ ulueke.  
\v 21 IĚ± paalaęž‰ pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ IĚ± pa ipuluaęž‰ dinaęž‰taęž‰ yaka Kodaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ wenoko mealieke. Kutupa IĚ±maęž‰taęž‰ mo ambaęž‰ hoke hau pimi wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kikanaęž‰ haumanu pimieki make ikaęž‰ hoke hone wimi ekimanu make ikaęž‰ loke apaęž‰taasaęž‰ hoke haumanu pimi ekimanu hoki na walemeke ekinaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ eĚ± lolueke hone witolome.   
\c 13  
\s1 Paeyaaso kinki pitaęž‰laęž‰ pimanu  
\p
\v 1 IĚ±taęž‰ hoto tepo peao iki handolo ipuluekemaęž‰ taapolome. Mo Baibolomaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰taęž‰ Maęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ ketete paęž‰laęž‰me lemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto mo hali yaapo tepomaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ Otaęž‰e Handomaęž‰me pi alo wekitisi haemekaęž‰naęž‰ homeke anaęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰me laęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 2 Ambaęž‰ hande hoto yaapo peao epoaęž‰ dinaęž‰ la kuaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ame papate halo dinaęž‰taęž‰ paa lolueke. Iki ameĚ±leĚ± ambaęž‰ hoke hau pimi wandaęž‰hali make pa iki paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ make IĚ±maęž‰ alo pi dupa. IĚ± paa ipuluaęž‰ dinaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ epi aęž‰ndaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ panisi meaęž‰peke ekitaęž‰ otaęž‰ pakaęž‰lao puaęž‰peke na yelieke alome.  
\v 3 Mo Ketisomaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ lo halaęž‰me ekinaęž‰ peneme yaasaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ otaęž‰ anaęž‰naęž‰ wia halimikie. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ piaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ damako na paęž‰laęž‰me. Kotoeki na pikitaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ iki tukiki paęž‰taęž‰manu ipikaęž‰ honkopu walo halaęž‰me.  
\v 4 Mo damako peaaso haenaęž‰ kone ipikitaęž‰ mo kotosinaęž‰ lu homaeyaęž‰pate Kodaęž‰naęž‰ honkopumaęž‰taęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ daęž‰taa hao halaęž‰me. Kutupa make ipiki ameĚ±leĚ± tunaaso hataęž‰ niki make damako polomaęž‰pate pa iki ameĚ±leĚ± tukikinaęž‰ hataęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ Ketiso wele peaasaęž‰eki maęž‰ndaęž‰ putupaęž‰ meaataęž‰ ikaęž‰ yankeke halumeke.   
\p
\v 5 Ikaęž‰ kone mo la handaęž‰laęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ u moneaaso hataęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone pi yokaalu peaęž‰paęž‰peke. Do hautaęž‰ ikaęž‰ otaęž‰ hone tulaasaęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ halemeo laa handaęž‰ uluekemaęž‰ peaęž‰paęž‰peke. Iki ambaęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± na lopemeketaęž‰ kotaęž‰ Yesu Ketisotaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ halaęž‰me hone u hapaęž‰peke aleo.  
\v 6 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ nikitaęž‰ na lopo halomaęž‰me laa hone uemenaęž‰ yeke IĚ±maęž‰ hone ti lao halome.  
\v 7 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ataęž‰kaęž‰ pikieki maęž‰ndaęž‰ na puemenaęž‰ laa nikanaęž‰maęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ yeni pu halomaęž‰me. Kotaęž‰ nikitaęž‰ mo la handaęž‰laęž‰eki lombei pumaęž‰me laa waluekemaęž‰ diaęž‰yaęž‰laęž‰me. Pate nikitaęž‰ lopo hake nono piomono kone ikitaęž‰ mo otaęž‰ tikitiki piki hau puemenaęž‰ yeke lomaęž‰me.  
\v 8 Nikanaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo otaęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰piki hau maęž‰ndaęž‰ homeke peaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰pate pa ipikaęž‰eki homeke pumanaęž‰ loaęž‰me.  
\v 9 Niki damako polomaęž‰ dinaęž‰taęž‰ iki honkopu hao haleme ekimaęž‰ nikitaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰ wopu paęž‰laęž‰me. Koto ekinaęž‰taęž‰ iki otaęž‰eki aęž‰ndaęž‰ na piki wandaęž‰hali hamenaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ yeni peaęž‰tiki pu halomaęž‰me.  
\v 10 Koto ekinaęž‰ yeketaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ papate hataęž‰ doeki laasome. Pa ekipeke IĚ± opolo epoaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± kaęž‰laęž‰ honkopu pitaęž‰ hataęž‰ iki tandapiki tupaęž‰ na aęž‰pa lolo polo tupaęž‰ loaęž‰me. Do honkoputaęž‰ iki mea londaęž‰laalo polo tupaęž‰ diaęž‰yaęž‰laęž‰pate iki mea daeyaluekemaęž‰ yeke loaęž‰me.   
\s1 Paeyaaso aęž‰talo pimanu  
\p
\v 11  Koto ekinaęž‰ ametaęž‰ yaka kame tonuo iki paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰taloe alome. Eki aęž‰ndaęž‰ otaęž‰ na piki wandaęž‰hali hamenaęž‰ iki otaęž‰ honkopu hao hapaęž‰peke. Yaka loaęž‰ honke pimanu opu hapaęž‰peke. Maęž‰ndaęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ ameĚ±leĚ± homeke hone u alualu peaęž‰paęž‰peke. Puki lopaniaasaęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ hapaęž‰peke. Kutupa mo pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki make puki lopaniaasaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ Kodaęž‰taęž‰ iki ameĚ±leĚ± halieke.   
\p
\v 12 Yankeke tonu paęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ kiki minaęž‰ alualu peaęž‰paęž‰peke. Do Kodaęž‰naęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ aęž‰talo pimanu tapaasememe.   
\p
\v 13 Tekehali Yesu Ketisonaęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homa tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ make Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰ make Holi Sipitidinaęž‰ taęž‰maęž‰ni pitaęž‰laęž‰eki paeyaomaęž‰taęž‰ iki ameĚ±leĚ± winaęž‰e.   